		{
			x: 17.0d
			y: 4.5d
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "Splitting the coin's two halves. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"A true scientist will use lots of elements to synthesize lots of amazing substances. Unfortunately, you'll have to obtain your own elements, as probably there's no place you can buy them from. Since Hydrogen and Oxygen are two essential elements, you'll be starting with them. Probably."
				""
				"Say \"hello\" to the Electrolytic Separator. This machine will take certain substances and will split them into their base components."
				""
				"The Electrolytic Separator is used to separate Heavy Water into Deuterium and Oxygen, Brine into Sodium and Chlorine, and Water into Hydrogen and Oxygen. The products will be used in other Mekanism machines/contraptions."
			]
			dependencies: ["41B717C98381E7DC"]
