		{
			x: 20.0d
			y: 3.0d
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "Cleaning things up. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"Dealing with a fair amount of Dirty Slurries? Want to throw them away 'cause they're useless? Have no way of cleaning them? Worry no more. The Chemical Washer is for you."
				""
				"This machine will be mainly used as part of the ore processing system. It will turn dirty slurries, into clean slurries which will later be processed in a Chemical Crystallizer."
				""
				"The most important role of this machine, will be played in the production of Uranium Crystals, which will be used to synthesize advanced fuels."
			]
			dependencies: ["40623128C431038D"]
			id: "141647BC0058E0D5"
			tasks: [{
				id: "38CF1696DA5375AD"
				type: "item"
				item: "mekanism:chemical_washer"
			}]
		}
		{
			x: 21.0d
			y: 7.0d
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "Yes, Mekanism has one, too. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"Unlike Industrial Foregoing's Dissolution Chamber, this one will only be used with Sulfuric Acid. It will be used to obtain base chemicals and dirty slurries for the ore quintupling process."
				""
				"It will use 100 mB of sulfuric acid for every ore dissolved and it will output 1000 mb of dirty slurry. This slurry needs washing in the Chemical Washer."
			]
			dependencies: ["40623128C431038D"]
			id: "2E83341A5C81DF78"
			tasks: [{
				id: "45A5E26321BDE39F"
				type: "item"
				item: "mekanism:chemical_dissolution_chamber"
			}]
		}
		{
			x: 19.0d
			y: 7.0d
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "A chemical situation. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"Forward, you'll mainly be interested into two things. These will be Sulfuric Acid and Uranium Hexafluoride. While the Acid will be used for ore quintupling, the Hexafluoride will be used as fuel. You'll need this machine in order to obtain these two gases."
				""
				"The Chemical Oxidizer accepts incoming materials to produce a variety of gases from them. It uses 80 RF/tick. It is a crucial machine needed for Mekanism's 5x ore production system."
			]
			dependencies: ["40623128C431038D"]
			id: "33040FC0EB0A4FD8"
			tasks: [{
				id: "131974808C0A7858"
				type: "item"
				item: "mekanism:chemical_oxidizer"
			}]
		}
		{
			x: 17.0d
			y: 7.0d
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "Enhancing that Osmium. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"Osmium is a very dense material, which is great, but it would be better if it was a little stronger. Maybe some obsidian could provide that missing strenght. Only if you had a way to combine the two.. Oh.. WAIT!"
				""
				"Yup, that's right, there it is. The Osmium Compressor. It is used to create Refined Obsidian Ingots from Refined Obsidian Dust and Glowstone Ingots from Glowstone Dust."
				""
				"It fuses liquid Osmium with the originating materials to create their corresponding ingots."
			]
			dependencies: ["41B717C98381E7DC"]
			id: "4E3C384D72C1DCAB"
			tasks: [{
				id: "214F8F3DDA55C4F0"
