				"The only place you can find Certus Quartz. It is also the place where the meteorites from the Overworld came from."
				""
				"Keep in mind that here you'll find Desh Ore, which will be required to build a better rocket."
				""
				"The Moon's ore list also includes Source Gems. These bright crystals will be used in Ars Nouveau to channel the magical energies around the world. "
