		{
			x: 11.0d
			y: 11.0d
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "Say \"hi\" to the Fluix Seed. These seeds can be tossed in water to start growing (don't worry, they won't despawn). When they're fully grown, you'll receive some Pure Fluix Crystals which will be used in other recipes. Make sure you use them in a Crystal Growth Unit, so you don't have to wait that much for them to grow"
			dependencies: ["631FBD2CC11F4972"]
