			subtitle: "We had no budget for Titanium :D Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"The Black Iron is a very malleable, yet very strong alloy, capable of making various shapes and withstand large amount of stress."
				""
				"You'll be able to use this material in lots of recipes, so make sure you have plenty of it in your stock."
