			description: [
				"Congrats! You maanged to obtain a great amount of Latex. Now what? Well, we're moving to the next step on the assembly line. To the Latex Processing Unit!"
				""
				"This amazing machine will use 100mb of Latex, 500mb of Water and a healty amount of RF/FE to produce 1 piece of Tiny Dry Rubber."
