			x: 19.0d
			y: 2.0d
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "Lithium dust can be considered the heart and soul of a true battery. Use this fine dust to make the elements required for an Induction Matrix, which essencially, is a very large, modular battery"
			dependencies: [
				"02502B52A16346C0"
